body: Everything that had happened to me since we'd last spoken:
1) Moved from Unranked to Iron 5 in Guild of Gods
2) Got a low B in my first microbiology test by drawing a smiling microscope with a thumbs-up extending from the stage.
3) Watched her friend Graham try to snort coke off of a porch balcony at a house party, only for it to blow away in the wind.
